com.generalnegentropics.archis.utils
Class IntegerHashtable

java.lang.Object
  com.generalnegentropics.archis.utils.IntegerHashtable
public class IntegerHashtable
extends java.lang.Object

A simple, fast, fixed-size hash table with int keys and object values.

This table is synchronized and thread-safe.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Adam Ierymenko
